docs.lead_paragraph: Henry Siegel yesterday authorized a statement to the effect that he had leased the ten-story building, running through from 56 West Fourteenth Street to 55 to 61 West Thirteenth Street, from Herman Sielcken, by whom the property was purchased a few days ago.

headline.main: HENRY SIEGEL'S STORE PLANS.; Acquires More Property at Fourteenth Street and Sixth Avenue -- To Open by Jan. 1, 1904.
